DelegatedWork.adminDescription: Allows the app to read the signed-in user's files.

DelegatedWork.adminDisplayName: Read files that the user selects (preview)

DelegatedWork.userDescription: (Preview) Allows the app to read, create, update and delete files in the application's folder.
